  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544550/extras/3128f7758136b159377ecde6feb3a34c.webp?t=1724261223\" width=597 height=38 /></span><br><br>Guidelicious is a short, interactive visual novel about waking up in a strange room with a mysterious man. <br><br>Engage in a fully voice acted story as every powerless move forward leads you closer to the truth of why you're here... hopefully.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544550/extras/83688c4783d05384b6daf3ea27b37c61.webp?t=1724261223\" width=597 height=38 /></span><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544550/extras/609380f867ffff52ebeb20802fe8aa32.webp?t=1724261223\" width=30 height=13 /></span> <1,000 words (10-15 minutes of playtime)!<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544550/extras/609380f867ffff52ebeb20802fe8aa32.webp?t=1724261223\" width=30 height=13 /></span> Fully voiced!<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544550/extras/609380f867ffff52ebeb20802fe8aa32.webp?t=1724261223\" width=30 height=13 /></span> 1 animated Guide + 1 interactive background!<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544550/extras/609380f867ffff52ebeb20802fe8aa32.webp?t=1724261223\" width=30 height=13 /></span> 5 endings!<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544550/extras/609380f867ffff52ebeb20802fe8aa32.webp?t=1724261223\" width=30 height=13 /></span> Nameable female protagonist!<br> <span cla